<heading>list - List all worlds.</heading>

<rule/>

<heading level="2">
Usage
</heading>

<pre>
  list
</pre>

<heading level="2">
Description
</heading>

<paragraph>
Lists all worlds with their ID, name and description.
</paragraph>

<heading level="2">
Examples
</heading>

<pre>
list
  List all worlds.
</pre>

